  "gameplayNotes": [
    "Characters use 4-direction movement (up/down/left/right); hero-character lacks right sprites - mirror left",
    "Terrain tiles are 16x16px; character sprites are larger (40x64 or 64x64) - scale or offset as needed",
    "Walls use 2x2 tile groups (tl/tr/bl/br) for proper corner rendering",
    "Doors have closed/open states; combine 4 tiles for full door",
    "Keys come in gold/silver/bronze tiers for progression-based locks",
    "Potions: red (health), blue (mana), green (stamina/status effect)",
    "Use floor variants (1/2/3/4) to add visual variety and break up repetition",
    "Consider adding NPC characters from alternative packs for dialogue/quests"
  ],

